                     <interp inst="t18131201-11-person175" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . After the receipt of that letter did you take any measures - A. It was suggested by Mr. 
               <persName id="t18131201-11-person176">
                  Charles 
                  Haigh
               <interp inst="t18131201-11-person176" type="surname" value="Haigh"></interp>
