                     <interp inst="t18131201-11-person176" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , to have a medical gentleman there, without Rhodes knowing of it. Mr. Haslam is the principal gentleman of Bethlem hospital. Mr. Haslam came and saw him once.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you learn from Rhodes whether he discovered what your object could be in having this person - A. I did. I have a letter here that points that out.</p>
               <p>COURT. Then Mr. Haslam did come and converse with him - A. He did, and after that I received this next letter from him.</p>
