            . Here is another letter, neither date or signature; the post mark is the 1st of December; I believe it to be his hand writing; it is not writ in his usual hand; it is addressed to Daniel Haigh, 6, Aldermanbury, Cheapside; it begins, to 
               <persName id="t18131201-11-person186">
                  Daniel 
                  Haigh
               <interp inst="t18131201-11-person186" type="surname" value="Haigh"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18131201-11-person186" type="given" value="Daniel"></interp>
